00:08.000 --> 00:09.669
<i>Previously on </i> Cloak and Dagger...

00:09.670 --> 00:11.169
You're lying and you know it!

00:11.170 --> 00:12.999
One of them shot Billy, I saw it.

00:13.000 --> 00:15.169
We've got no evidence of that.

00:15.170 --> 00:16.499
Enough already, Ma.

00:16.500 --> 00:18.119
You're afraid if I don't do everything

00:18.120 --> 00:20.079
just right, you're gonna lose me.

00:20.080 --> 00:22.999
Find rich kids, slip a little
somethin' into their drinks,

00:23.000 --> 00:25.249
<i>and jack them of their rich-kid stuff.</i>

00:25.250 --> 00:27.169
<i>I got pinched. Tandy, I put all my money</i>

00:27.170 --> 00:29.379
<i>into your new life. I need your help.</i>

00:29.380 --> 00:30.922
All this anger inside of me.

00:30.947 --> 00:32.996
What if I could find the
person who caused it?

00:33.021 --> 00:35.310
<i>It's not anger
in the bottle. It's poison.</i>

00:35.335 --> 00:37.169
Can I get a fifth
of the O'Harren's, please?

00:37.170 --> 00:39.829
- I like making girlfriend pancakes.
- I'm your girlfriend?

00:39.830 --> 00:41.249
This was the kid, right?

00:41.250 --> 00:44.459
<i>Hopped that yellow banister
and then disappeared.</i>

00:44.460 --> 00:45.829
<i>I killed you and buried you.</i>

00:45.830 --> 00:47.872
Detective Connors, you're under arrest

00:47.897 --> 00:49.687
for the murder of Billy Johnson.

00:51.309 --> 00:53.178
